metadata.name: Bee Capsule
metadata.description:
The Bee Capsule represents a new chapter, a shift in my life and art.

Bees are capable of changing any ecosystem into a new and colorful one. 

I decided to make this my genesis piece for "Two Walls" because it's the piece that made me change the way I create and continue to build forward in amazing experience we call life.

In between just Two Walls life can happen, colors may emerge and stories will be made and told.

Dimensions:  2580px x 3060px
